    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "SAC Bannister of the Butte Office called at noon today and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "stated that a [REDACTED] Twin Falls,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "Idaho, at 2:45 a.m. Mountain Time today heard a noise in the back of b7c [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "her home. She thought a collision had occurred and investigated and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "found in the back yard of the home next door an object described as follows:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "A disc 30½\" in diameter, circular in shape, it is dished like a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "saucer and actually there is a saucer within a saucer in the manner of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "cymbals. On one surface there is attached a plastic dome described as about",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "14\" in diamter and affixed by 8 bolts in a rather rough manner. The bolts",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "can best be described as similar to stove bolts. On the other surface is",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "another dome of metal which is gold in color on one side and on the inside is",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "silver in color, which looks like tin. Through the plastic dome can be ob-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "served three tubes similar to radio tubes and there is some wiring. The disc",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "generally is 10\" thick and at the point where the domes are located about",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "14\" in thickness. There is an object on it similar to electric coil which",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "has some type of an arm on it and bears the words \"Inspected TS\". Some of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "the wiring has been burned off and it looks as though something might be",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "missing.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "[REDACTED] stated that if this were the work of some prankster",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "he went to quite a bit of trouble. He stated the press is aware of this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "incident. He stated that the disc had been picked up and was now at the b7c",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "Police Department, Twin Falls, Idaho. He was instructed to notify the local",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "Army authorities of the existence of this disc.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
